        <item>
            <title>Version 0.15.0</title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                    <h2>What's New in 0.15.0</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>"Hey Viska" wake word detection is now more reliable and handles more speech variations.</li>
                        <li>The recording panel now shows clear color-coded status icons so you always know what the app is doing.</li>
                        <li>Voice commands now cover more settings — switch AI mode, output style, and more by speaking.</li>
                        <li>Silence detection automatically kicks in after a wake word trigger, so recording stops when you finish speaking.</li>
                        <li>Stability and performance improvements.</li>
                    </ul>
                ]]>
